um) saplings (1979) Am. J. Bot., 66, pp. 441-5; Stinson, K.A., Natural selection favors rapid reproductive phenology in Potentilla pulcherrima (Rosaceae) at opposite ends of a subalpine snowmelt gradient (2004) Am. J. Bot., 91, pp. 531-9; Veblen, T.T., Stand dynamics in Chilean Nothofagus forests (1985) The Ecology of Natural Disturbance and Patch Dynamics, pp. 35-51. , In: (eds. S. T. A. Picket. P. S. White). pp. Academic Press, New York; Veblen, T.T., Ashton, D.H., Successional pattern above timberline in South-Central Chile (1979) Vegetatio, 40, pp. 39-47; Zar, J.H., (1996) Biostatistical Analysis., , Prentice Hall, New York","Premoli, A.C.; Laboratorio Ecotono, CRUB-Universidad Nacional del Comahue, Quintral 1250, Bariloche 8400, Argentina; email: apremoli@crub.uncoma.edu.ar",,,,,,,,14429985,,AUECF,,"English","Austral Ecol.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-34250730724
